# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.3.0] - 2021-11-12

### Added
- Add chapter "Project Structure" in README file which explicates the brief function of each file
- Add headline "p2m3 has finished" in README file

## [0.2.3] - 2021-11-12

### Added
- Add chapter "About the advanced-mode project (with GTK support)" in README file which introduces the bonus part of the project with GTK support
- Update the CHANGELOG to record changes made to the project
- Indent all codes

## [0.2.2] - 2021-11-11

### Edited
-Revise the code so that it could pass the JOJ compilation test

### Removed
- Remove unnecessary annoatation in the project

## [0.2.1] - 2021-11-10

### Added
- Add chapter "About the simple-mode project (without GTK support)" in README file which introduces the functioning of the project without GTK

### Removed
- Remove printing of the shuffling result and the dealing result to each player


## [0.1.2] - 2021-11-7

### Changed
- Change the strategy to enable and disable GTK mode by establish a new GTK_ENABLED.h file which will not comflict with all of the existing files.
- Update the CHANGELOG to record changes made to the project
- Indent all codes

## [0.1.1] - 2021-11-5

### Added
- Add necessary function in "mgtk.c" to ensure the whole GTK version works smoothly
- Add content "mandatory part" and "bonus part" in README file to keep full track of the schedule

### Changed
- Change the original function "animation" "read_pile" "read_table" to adapt GTK mode
- Update the CHANGELOG to record changes made to the project
- Indent all codes

## [0.1.0] - 2021-11-1

### Added
- Add related gtk package in CMakeLists.txt to make sure the gtk function works well
- Add file "mgtk.c" as well as "mgtk.h" to enact GUI programming
- Add macro sign GTK to make functions work differently in GTK and none-GTK mode.

### Changed
- Update the CHANGELOG to record changes made to the project
- Indent all codes

### Removed
- Remove empty sections from CHANGELOG
- Remove all unnecessary spaces

## [0.0.6] - 2021-10-21

### Added
- Add file 'log.c' and 'log.h' to manipulate operation with the log file
- Add several log related function in log.c
- Add the headline, the basic introduction part as well as the mandatory work part in the README file


## [0.0.5] - 2021-10-19
### Added
- README section on function list.
- Headline of the README file

### Changed
- Update the CHANGELOG to record changes made to the project


## [0.0.4] - 2021-10-17
### Added
- function animation (file 'animation.c')
- file animation.c
- file animation.h
- related sub-function for function animation (file 'animation.c')

### Changed
- Update the CHANGELOG to record changes made to the project
- Indent all codes

### Removed
- Remove empty sections from CHANGELOG
- Remove all unnecessary spaces 


## [0.0.3] - 2021-10-13
### Added
- memory clearing at the end of each round
- optimizing round settings to minimize the influence a round could cause to the following round

### Changed
- Simply the function main by remove irrelevant codes to other places (e.g 'init_vars.m') and add annotations to it
- Add annotations to functions
- Add necessary annotations to codes in order to be more reader-friendly

### Removed
- Remove empty sections from the project


## [0.0.2] - 2021-10-11
### Added
- function main (file 'main.c')
- basic properties handled in one file (file 'basic_property.h')
- input handling
- type card_pile (as a queue)
- function related to basic manipulation of the type card_pile
- type player (as a structure)
- type table (as a two-direction rounded linked list)

## [0.0.1] - 2021-10-10
### Added
- This CHANGELOG file to hopefully serve as a record for ENGR151 project 2.
